channel.title: What Should I Get For My B-Day
channel.description:
EDIT!!!: I just found this REALLLLLLY cool thing. It's a mp3/mp4/digital camera/voice recorder/pic viewer/AM/FM Tuner/Radio Recorder. The only catch is it's only two gigs, and my library is almost to 20. I found it on Tiger Direct [url=http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/SearchTools/item-details.asp?EdpNo=3172650&CatId=15]HERE[/url]. Please tell me what you think of it, and if I should get something else. Thanks. __________________________________________________
Hey,
Here's another decision that I'm trusting to my favorite online community =) ... My birthday is July 23rd(I'll be 15.), and I have no idea what I want. My parents say that I am past the surprise thing, and say that they have no fucking idea what I want, I told them I feel the same way. I have interests in a few things, but honestly, I don't really want anything at the moment. They're giving me a $100 fund, and they say that I can't just have the cash... For some reason.. I don't want it. PS, I know, the last Harry Potter book is coming out 2 days before my birthday, I'm going to be first in line at 12:00am, but I convinced my parents that the book shouldn't be my present because they would have gotten it for me even if it wasn't my birthday because I'm obsessed with HP, and have been reading them since 3rd grade.
Here are my interests, maybe you can help me find something good:
[ul][li]SlipKnot[/li] [li]Insane Clown Posse[/li] [li]Harry Potter[/li] [li]TRIPP Clothing[/li] [li]Death Metal[/li] [li]Computers[/li] [li]Wicca & Witchcraft[/li] [li]Little Cool Ass Knick Knacks and Widgets[/li] [li]I'm Starting to become partial to mp3/mp4 players since mine got stolen...[/li][/ul]
That's about all I can think of... I have a pretty good computer... Here are my specs:
[ul][li]1gb Ram[/li] [li]3.0ghz Dual Core Processor[/li] [li]232gb hard drive[/li][/ul]
So I really don't have a need to update my computer because it's good enough for what I do(code, graphics, games, music, videos).
Well, my parents say that I can go online and shop, so you guys can tell me good deals online, or just suggest some things.
[center]Any NICE input is appreciated. Thanks,[/center]
Buzzy
